snippet.title: Planet Strike // Teaser
snippet.description:
Play the Game ► https://store.steampowered.com/app/3137000/Planet_Strike/

Experience the ultimate cosmic billiards. Solar winds that accelerate planets with intrusion. Asteroids decelerating on impact. Lead the planets of the solar system to the black hole by utilizing various devices placed in the field.

Developed by @danboruman
